{"tid":2329280,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"BLACKPINK JISOO收到人生第一個咖啡車應援！原來是好姐妹ROSÉ送的","createTime":"2020-12-17T06:33:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T23:42:45.000Z","uid":16659,"like":45,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"7a38c39541b8aa6be8531314e9bd4dbac22c55af","tid":2329280,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T06:33:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_b06ba2a7aacabcbb888042e0ccbfc906/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-16/132372-889193.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_b06ba2a7aacabcbb888042e0ccbfc906%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-16%2F132372-889193.png&h=993ce456&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBLACKPINK成員ROS&Eacute;給隊友JISOO送來了咖啡車，讓好姐妹十分感動。<br />\n<br />\nJISOO通過自己的個人IG發佈最新近況，寫道：「我人生中的第一部咖啡車的主人公是朴羅婕（ROS&Eacute;）」，同時還曬出了多張ROS&Eacute;送來的應援咖啡車的認證照。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n照片裡，ROS&Eacute;正在JTBC 電視劇《雪滴花》拍攝現場與ROSE所送的咖啡車一起合影。 她穿著黑色大衣，圍著厚厚的圍巾，對著鏡頭露出甜美的笑容。 咖啡車上則寫著給JISOO應援的文字，希望劇組的所有人看到JISOO都能夠打起精神。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_a168e16e37bbe5b36868a56964300b7d/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-16/132372-889194.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_a168e16e37bbe5b36868a56964300b7d%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-16%2F132372-889194.jpg&h=60d90e37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_dbfb9b3e6f0c7d980586c96c228a8599/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-16/132372-889195.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_dbfb9b3e6f0c7d980586c96c228a8599%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-16%2F132372-889195.jpg&h=bf7227cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_2432238a4ba1d2d3e37be292891846b0/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-16/132372-889196.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_2432238a4ba1d2d3e37be292891846b0%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-16%2F132372-889196.jpg&h=2df00dba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_bab5e295f56bb37f62399529d9b8e2fa/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-16/132372-889197.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_bab5e295f56bb37f62399529d9b8e2fa%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-16%2F132372-889197.png&h=3613941e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由JISOO和丁海寅、金惠奫一起合作的《雪滴花》由《SKY Castle》的導演趙賢卓與編劇俞賢美攜手打造，將於2021年和觀眾見面。"},{"pid":"5c78ea788358f3a962dc74523a32cfc114be9542","tid":2329280,"uid":234509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T06:34:59.000Z","msg":"Jisoo b<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c884d5f198aaa91deb5b8b7565b5f949d646c2c","tid":2329280,"uid":229026,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T06:35:03.000Z","msg":"感情很好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29a84dc4a5cd1a4314d6d0ff74fdd0ea109ec9a7","tid":2329280,"uid":165368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T06:42:52.000Z","msg":"偷我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />po啲圖?"},{"pid":"f23ddfa9f6fc22cfb666fb602c4e243449c3ad31","tid":2329280,"uid":320204,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T06:53:33.000Z","msg":"我想色jisoo<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0dc5cd1396cd12061bd30340b361b0bc7d62bf5","tid":2329280,"uid":382422,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f23ddfa9f6fc22cfb666fb602c4e243449c3ad31","tid":2329280,"uid":320204,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T06:53:33.000Z","msg":"我想色jisoo<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12